A 和 Kayla Oaddams。" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Iggy-Pop-and-Tyler-The-Creator.-Credits-CARL-DE-SOUZA-and-Kayla-Oaddams.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Iggy-Pop-and-Tyler-The-Creator.-Credits-CARL-DE-SOUZA-and-Kayla-Oaddams-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Iggy-Pop-and-Tyler-The-Creator.-Credits-CARL-DE-SOUZA-and-Kayla-Oaddams-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Iggy-Pop-and-Tyler-The-Creator.-Credits-CARL-DE-SOUZA-and-Kayla-Oaddams-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Iggy-Pop-and-Tyler-The-Creator.-Credits-CARL-DE-SOUZA-and-Kayla-Oaddams-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Iggy-Pop-and-Tyler-The-Creator.-Credits-CARL-DE-SOUZA-and-Kayla-Oaddams-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/iggy-pop">伊基·波普 (Iggy Pop)</a>在他最新的 BBC 6 音乐广播节目中称赞<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tyler-the-creator">泰勒，造物主</a>是一位“真正的老派天才”。</p><p>在他的节目<em>《Iggy Confidential》</em>中，这位朋克传奇人物回忆了他与这位说唱歌手一起“一天工作”的时光——他们俩都<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-iggy-pop-aap-rocky-and-tyler-the-creator-goof-around-for-gucci-advert-2764730">出现在了 A$AP Rocky 的 Gucci 广告活动中</a>。</p><p>在 Harmony Korine 执导的视频中，穿着西装和靴子的摇滚和嘻哈明星在西海岸的一处家里闲逛，一边吃意大利面，一边在浴室里跳舞。</p><p>泰勒似乎给伊基波普留下了深刻的印象，正如他在广播中所说：“我一直很喜欢泰勒。有一次我和他一起工作了一天，他会尽一切努力来引起注意。他也是一位真正的全能歌曲、舞蹈和作家天才——一位真正的老派天才与新派方法。”</p><p>听下面的完整剪辑。您可以<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03yblbx" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>找到 Iggy Pop 的 Radio 6 音乐节目。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DEfDMq3qGWw/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-